casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Jacqueline Dela CRUZ, Appellant. WD 49176 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: September 18, 2018 Kent Gipson, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Taylor Rickard, Kansas City, MO, Co-Counsel for Appellant. Karen Kramer, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division One: Thomas H. Newton, P.J., Gary D. Witt, and Anthony Rex Gabbert, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Ms. Jacqueline Dela Cruz appeals her conviction following a bench trial in Jackson County Circuit Court of eleven counts relating to the abuse and death of her nephew's daughter. The court sentenced her to concurrent terms of imprisonment on each count including two life terms. We affirm in accordance with Rule 30.25(b).
